codex
I have the rewrite strategy: make the verifier execute all three exploit stages in order, verify the victim’s fungible claim on-chain, and keep the old “observe existing” shortcut only as a last-resort infeasibility case instead of the main path. I’m updating `src/FlawVerifier.sol` now.
